improvements.title: Stream Processor v0.5.6
description: The new version `v0.5.6` of the _Stream Processor_ is available!
This version includes enhanced CI for v branches and improved error handling that removes hard fail on console.log buffer exceeded.
For more information check out the service [changelog](/docs/products/fast_data_v2/stream_processor/changelog).

improvements.title: Farm Data v0.5.5
description: The new version `v0.5.5` of the _Farm Data_ is available!
This version includes new MongoDB configuration capabilities with implementation of mongodb config from connections and new MongodbConnectionConfig support.
For more information check out the service [changelog](/docs/products/fast_data_v2/farm_data/changelog).

improvements.title: Back-Lit Library
description: The new version `v1.5.25` of the back-kit library is available!
Refer to back-kit [changelog](/docs/products/microfrontend-composer/back-kit/changelog) for finer-grained details of new versions.

bugFixes: Fixed `formOptions.isPartialFormat` management and output in filters, export and bk-form-wizard
